# Installation Instructions

To build and install RELB from source, follow these steps:

1. Generate the build system files:
   aclocal
   autoconf
   autoheader
   automake --add-missing

2. Configure the build for your system:
   ./configure

3. Compile the source code:
   make

4. (Optional) Install the binaries (may require root privileges):
   make install

For additional configuration options, run:
   ./configure --help

See the README.md for more information about configuration and usage.